CLASS

public static final RdfType CLASS
A class. If a node X is a class, the existence of this triple is implied: <X rdfs:subClassOf rdfs:Resource>

PROPERTY

public static final RdfType PROPERTY
A property. If a node X is a property, the existence of this triple is implied: <X rdf:type rdf:Property>
